&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;display: none; max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://px.ads.linkedin.com/collect/?pid=3639242&amp;amp;conversionId=6145458&amp;amp;fmt=gif&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Are you energized by building high-performing teams, improving complex systems, and creating scalable operations that deliver exceptional results? Join our award-winning company and culture as a General Manager, Warehouse &amp;amp; Facilities and play a key role in shaping the future of our distribution operations, facilities, and leadership team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is responsible for leading a safe, scalable, high-performing distribution center by strengthening leadership capability, optimizing operational systems, and driving continuous improvement that supports our Brand Promise and long-term business growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll be doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Aligning with &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://clickstop.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/The-Clickstop-Code.pdf&quot;&gt;Clickstop’s Core Values&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; to drive our culture and business forward.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In this role, Responsible, Decisive, Courageous, and Strategic stand out.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building and developing leaders who create accountability, engagement, and operational excellence throughout the organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Driving fulfillment, inventory, facilities, safety, and operational performance while balancing current needs with future scalability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifying opportunities to improve systems, processes, and infrastructure through data-driven decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating across departments to align operational execution with broader business goals and customer outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;General Manager Critical Skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Strategic Judgment &amp;amp; Business Prioritization&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make sound decisions across people, performance, cost, and operational investments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balance short-term execution with long-term business scalability and growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1; padding-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;Enables: Better strategic decisions and stronger long-term business performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Systems Thinking &amp;amp; Operational Design&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand how people, inventory flow, labor, technology, and customer outcomes interact across the operation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify root causes and improve end-to-end systems rather than isolated processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;padding-left: 40px; line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;Enables: Greater scalability, operational efficiency, and sustainable performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Leadership Through Leaders &amp;amp; Culture Stewardship&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop leaders who create accountability, engagement, and strong team performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a culture of ownership, trust, continuous improvement, and shared success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;padding-left: 40px; line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;Enables: Strong leadership depth, consistent execution, and organizational stability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Change Leadership &amp;amp; Continuous Improvement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead operational improvements across multiple teams, functions, and systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive sustainable change through process improvements, technology, and leadership development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
